BHOP_VOXEL

A map in the "voxel(ish)" style. This map took a while as i worked more on making the map feel more environmental with little to no "bhop blocks" eg. just 64u squares.

CHANGE HDRLEVEL TO "MAT_HDR_LEVEL 2" IF EXPERIENCING FULLBRIGHT  (FIXED 15/9/19)

Main map: 1:30 min
Bonus: 23-25 sec
